# Toast — Styles

## Class structure
- `.acko-toast-region` — fixed position container, `z-index: var(--z-toast)`, `pointer-events: none`
- `.acko-toast-region > *` — re-enable pointer events on each toast
- `.acko-toast` — individual item, `border-radius: 20px`, `box-shadow: 0px 2px 16px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04)`
- `.acko-toast-icon` — leading icon, `shrink-0`, top-aligned
- `.acko-toast-content` — flex column, title + description
- `.acko-toast-title` — `font-size: var(--font-body-sm-size)`, weight 600
- `.acko-toast-description` — same size, opacity 0.85
- `.acko-toast-action` — underlined text button, same color as toast
- `.acko-toast-dismiss` — `width/height: var(--scale-24)`, opacity 0.6 → 1 on hover

## Position variants
| Class | Position |
|-------|---------|
| `.acko-toast-region-top-right` | `top: var(--scale-20); right: var(--scale-20)` |
| `.acko-toast-region-top-left` | `top: var(--scale-20); left: var(--scale-20)` |
| `.acko-toast-region-top-center` | `top: var(--scale-20); left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%)` |
| `.acko-toast-region-bottom-right` | `bottom: var(--scale-20); right: var(--scale-20)` |
| `.acko-toast-region-bottom-left` | `bottom: var(--scale-20); left: var(--scale-20)` |
| `.acko-toast-region-bottom-center` | `bottom: var(--scale-20); left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%)` |

## Variant colors
| Variant | Border | Background | Text |
|---------|--------|-----------|------|
| `info` | `--color-info-border` | `--color-info-subtle` | `--color-info-text` |
| `success` | `--color-success-border` | `--color-success-subtle` | `--color-success-text` |
| `warning` | `--color-warning-border` | `--color-warning-subtle` | `--color-warning-text` |
| `error` | `--color-error-border` | `--color-error-subtle` | `--color-error-text` |

## Animation
`acko-toast-in`: `opacity 0, translateY(var(--scale-8)) → opacity 1, translateY(0)`, 250ms `--ease-out-quart`
